2 Building the model

We can now build a model

## Analysis of Deviance Table (Type II tests)
## 
## Response: admit
##      LR Chisq Df Pr(>Chisq)    
## gre    4.1071  1    0.04270 *  
## gpa    5.8508  1    0.01557 *  
## rank  21.5437  3  8.116e-05 ***
## ---
## Signif. codes:  0 '***' 0.001 '**' 0.01 '*' 0.05 '.' 0.1 ' ' 1

As we can see, all predictors in our model are significant.

So final model is the following:

admit = 0.0197617 + gre * 2.2131891 + gpa * 2.2131891 + rank2 0.5086194 + rank3 0.2628151 + rank4 * 0.2147147
